# Update a book
PUT http://localhost:3001/books/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Making the New America - Part II"
}

### 

# Delete a book
DELETE http://localhost:3001/books/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json